    {
      "datasource": "mysql",
      "description": "Raw reviewer and author minutes aggregated over the selected period for the top 20 engineers by total reviewer minutes. Exposes engineers who do significant review work whether or not they author PRs. The combined_ratio column uses NULLIF so pure reviewers (no authored minutes) appear as NULL in the ratio column while still surfacing at the top of the table.",
